include ../layout/_head

body
  include ../partials/_navbar

  block content
    //- HERO SECTION
    section.hero.about-hero
      .hero-content.about-hero-content
        .hero-txt
          h1 About Us
          p Learn how Kobciye Foundation is transforming communities and creating hope, one project at a time.

    //- ABOUT SECTION
    section.about-us
      .section-divider
        .divider-line
        .divider-label About Kobciye
        .divider-line

      .about-cards-container
        .about-card
          .about-card-icon
            i.fa-solid.fa-flag
          h2 Our Story
          p Our story began with a simple desire to make a difference in the lives of those who need it most. We started as a small initiative and have grown into a community-driven organization committed to creating meaningful impact. Guided by compassion and the belief that change starts locally, we work closely with communities to understand their needs and provide practical, sustainable solutions.

        .about-card
          .about-card-icon
            i.fa-solid.fa-bullseye
          h2 Our Mission
          p Our mission is driven by a commitment to support and uplift vulnerable individuals and communities. We focus on providing essential resources, opportunities, and guidance that improve lives and create lasting change. Guided by compassion and responsibility, we work hand in hand with communities to address real needs and promote sustainable development.

        .about-card
          .about-card-icon
            i.fa-solid.fa-eye
          h2 Our Vision
          p Our vision is to create a world where every individual has access to opportunity, dignity, and support. We aspire to build strong, inclusive communities where people are empowered to grow, thrive, and shape their own futures. Guided by unity and resilience, we strive for sustainable change that is impactful and shared across generations.

    //- TEAM MEMBERS SECTION
    section.team
      .section-divider
        .divider-line
        .divider-label Meet Our Team
        .divider-line

      .team-wrapper
        button.scroll-btn.left
          i.fa-solid.fa-chevron-left

        .team-container
          if members && members.length > 0
            each member in members
              .team-card
                .team-card-img
                  img(src=`/uploads/members/${member.memberImage}` alt=member.name)
                .team-card-info
                  h3.team-name= member.name
                  p.team-role= member.role
          else
            p.empty-state No team members found.

        button.scroll-btn.right
          i.fa-solid.fa-chevron-right

    //- TESTIMONIALS
    section.testimonials
      .section-divider
        .divider-line
        .divider-label What People Said About Us
        .divider-line
      .testimonial-cards
        .testimonial-card
          .quote-icon "
          p "Kobciye helped my community get clean water. Truly life-changing!"
          h3 — Amina, Nairobi
        .testimonial-card
          .quote-icon "
          p "Volunteering here taught me the value of giving back."
          h3 — John, Volunteer

    //- IMPACTS
    .section-divider
      .divider-label Our Impact
    section.impact-stats
      .stat
        .stat-icon
          i.fa-solid.fa-people-group
        h2 200+
        p Communities Served
      .stat
        .stat-icon
          i.fa-solid.fa-circle-check
        h2 50+
        p Projects Completed
      .stat
        .stat-icon
          i.fa-solid.fa-hands-holding-child
        h2 500+
        p Volunteers Engaged

    //- CALL ON ACTION
    section.get-involved
      h1 Get Involved
      p Join us in making a real difference in people's lives. Your support matters.
      a.get-involved-btn(href="/payment") Get Involved

  include ../partials/_footer

  script(src="/js/about.js")
  script(src="/js/main.js")